              "free_text": [
                " The experimental error is estimated to be",
                "about 5%  throughout the energy interval covered. The",
                "errors contributing to the results are of two",
                "different characters. One group consists of",
                "uncertainties inherent in the counting process and the",
                "experimental apparatus, that should be consider",
                " (i) counting statistics,",
                " (ii) monitoring,",
                " (iii) resolution,",
                " (iv) instability and non-linearity and",
                " (v) self-absorption in the backing material.",
                "The other group contains the errors due to treatment",
                "of the experimental data going from primary results to",
                "desired physical information, i.e. contributions as",
                " (vi) secondary effects in the detector,",
                " (vii) uncertainty in normalizing factors,",
                " (viii) deviations from theoretical assumptions and",
                " (ix) ambiguity of theoretical interpretation."
              ]
